title: Castle Of Doom (Vampyr)
description:
May 6 1932


A traveler obsessed with the supernatural visits an old inn and finds evidence of vampires.



Director:Carl Theodor Dreyer (as Carl Th. Dreyer)

Writers:Sheridan Le Fanu (based on a book by), Christen Jul (screenplay)

Stars:Julian West, Maurice Schutz, Rena Mandel





This is the English version of Vampyr.It's a VHS rip of an 80 year old movie so it's not the best quality.
